name: The H.R GIGER
description: In the past, I have had my art compared to the Legendary H.R. Giger, who is known for his biomechanical style of art and his contribution to the visionary design that inspired the art for the movie Alien. It's a huge honor and when I saw this I immediately thought of him. Forever honored to have my art compared to him. Feels good man. I made 5 because his birthday is on Feb 5.
